{
  "stem": "964.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the word came back that, since you're willing to work with us, you're more valuable to be on the-- on the-- in the plant, since the front comes-- comes towards-- towards this town, and to give them information that they would require.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So the information they ask-- because in this plant where we worked, we used to fix tanks, trucks, all the paraphernalia from the-- from the front.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the soldiers, when they came in a truck or a tank, the crew came-- came with them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They remained with the tank as long as we fix it, and then they went back to the front.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So while we worked with them, we could find out what-- when did they leave Germany, how many was in the company, where did they fight, what kind of fight, what the moral situation is, mental situation in the German Army.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "All these things we relayed to-- to that-- we-- we had a girl that did-- did the contact with the other guy.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because he couldn't expose himself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But he was-- probably he was, since he was a communist in the-- in the-- in the old days, he couldn't be-- he couldn't move around too much.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So anyway, that girl took the message for-- forth and back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there was once a message that we-- they're looking for boots.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They need boots for the partisans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Since we knew that guy, that Hans, where we got the uniforms, we went over to him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we knew that he-- he likes to drink.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was the only one in that place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we took a bottle of schnapps, and we took some salami.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we told Hans, look, we need about 10 pair of boots.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Can you give it to us?",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
